There are two ways to upgrade the firmware of the device

A. OTA Update
  1. Navigate to your device via your favorite web browser
  2. Scroll down to *FIRMWARE UPDATE (OTA)* section, this includes an auto update check.
  3. Click the Install v.X.X.X button
  4. Profit!

B. Manual Update (In case OTA doesnt work or you want to revert to an older version)
  1. Navigate to your device via your favorite web browser
  2. Scroll down to *FIRMWARE UPDATE (OTA)* section.
  3. Under Manual Firmware Update select Choose File, and select your firmware.bin
  4. Click Flash Firmware
  5. Profit!
